{"_path":"/articles/vscode-nav","_dir":"articles","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"⌨️ VSCode全键盘操作指南","description":"本文介绍了在一个典型VSCode工作流程中，如何配置及使用全键盘操作。","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"前言"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"前言"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"写给想在编码工作中减少鼠标使用，提高编码效率的开发。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"我从小就玩射击游戏，所以对鼠标可谓是有天然依赖，但自几年前犯了一次鼠标手，不得不逐渐把一些右手操作分摊到左手。本来是琢磨着如何减轻右手的鼠标依赖，但没想到在这个过程中，我发现了全键盘操作的乐趣，编码体验意外提升不少。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"几年来，我的键位操作逐渐固定，并经受住包括使用不同键位键盘、切换不同操作系统（MacOS、Windows）w的考验。在此，将经验及技巧记录成文，包含了包括 VSCode 部分默认快捷键、自定义快捷键以及相关软件或插件介绍，希望能帮助到有类似需求的各位。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"提前回答一些问题"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"提前回答一些问题"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"为什么不使用 Vim？"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"理由很简单，当我把右手食指放到"},{"type":"element","tag":"kbd","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"j"}]},{"type":"text","value":"时，我的中指和无名指分别在"},{"type":"element","tag":"kbd","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"i"}]},{"type":"text","value":"和"},{"type":"element","tag":"kbd","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"o"}]},{"type":"text","value":"上。也许是中指比食指长了不少的缘故，"},{"type":"element","tag":"kbd","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"hjkl"}]},{"type":"text","value":"作为方向键对我来说太别扭了，远不如"},{"type":"element","tag":"kbd","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"wasd"}]},{"type":"text","value":"直观。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"为什么不是XXX（WebStorm、Visual Studio）？"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"要系统学